ygData.messageBody:
On Thu, 9 Sep 1999, CMai wrote:
>
> I used the song all the time in HighKeep since I got it (now lvl 35 hell).
> It is a cool song but I did not see that I get ultravision at all.

Isn't Highkeep pretty well lit? I didn't notice anything when
I first tried the song outdoors during day, but when I tried
it in a semi-dark portion of Runnyeye, everything got brighter
and picked up that bluish tint I get from Concord. In fact,
my first reaction was that I'd memorized the wrong song and
I spent a good 10 seconds wondering why there wasn't an eye
icon on my hotkeys or my screen.

--
